ection of open flux in coronal holes likely contributes to the\nrecognized deficit in solar open flux, but is unlikely to resolve it.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Mar 2021 02:52:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-08"}
