 dimension-dependent\nthreshold values, again the positional order is lost with a concomitant\ntransition to a phase with short range order. Large values of the order\nparameter - strain couplings can turn the phase transition into a first order\nas well.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Mar 2021 14:16:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Mar 2022 16:51:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 9 Aug 2022 18:51:28 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 30 Dec 2022 19:43:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-03"}
